Follow these steps to when using cryptsetup-luks:

Creating
~~~~~~~~

1. cryptsetup luksFormat /dev/partition
2. cryptsetup luksOpen /dev/partition label
3. mke2fs -j /dev/mapper/label
4. mount /dev/mapper/label /mnt/label

Mounting
~~~~~~~~

Of course later you don't have to use lunkFormat and mke2fs:

1. cryptsetup luksOpen /dev/partition label
2. mount /dev/mapper/label /mnt/label

Umounting
~~~~~~~~~

1. umount /mnt/label
2. cryptsetup luksClose label

Really simple :-)
